First, iVXjs needs to get experience information from the experience plugin
Second, once an experience is pulled in, iVXjs needs to
validate that the experience is valid to run this experience.
Once the data is validated, it pulls in all the modules that are required
for this experience and sets up the experience with the correct modules.
